## Database Operations

### Common Database Tasks

```bash
# Create new database
psql -h {{primary_db_ip}} -U postgres -c "CREATE DATABASE newdb OWNER {{db_user}};"

# Create new user
psql -h {{primary_db_ip}} -U postgres -c "CREATE USER newuser WITH PASSWORD 'securepassword';"

